BusyBox third-party binary
==========================

File: third_party/busybox-i386-static

Source:
  https://busybox.net/downloads/binaries/1.35.0-i686-linux-musl/busybox

Version: BusyBox 1.35.0 (i686, statically linked against musl)

License: GPL-2.0 (BusyBox)
  See https://busybox.net/license.html
  Full source: https://busybox.net/downloads/

Refresh:
  python scripts/fetch_busybox.py

pyOS also ships a small freestanding ash (built via scripts/build_ash.py)
used as /init when a full BusyBox ash session needs more kernel APIs.
The BusyBox binary is installed at /bin/busybox in the rootfs.
